A_s = 8 \times \pi \big(\frac{D}{2} \big)^2 = 2\pi D^2A_s = 8 \times \pi \big(\frac{D}{2} \big)^2 = 2\pi D^2
A_c = (dimension \times dimension) - 2\pi D^2A_c = (dimension \times dimension) - 2\pi D^2
\sigma_c = \frac{F_c}{A_c} = \frac{F-Fs}{A_c} = \frac{F-(\sigma_sA_s)}{A_c}\sigma_c = \frac{F_c}{A_c} = \frac{F-Fs}{A_c} = \frac{F-(\sigma_sA_s)}{A_c}

